transcript:
so let's be real if you died tonight
your employer would advertise to fill
your job role by the end of this week
and if not the end of this week the end
of this month but your loved ones your
family your friends would miss you
forever so the important thing I think
people need to understand is you don't
want to get so busy making a living that
you actually forget to make a life
